{
 "name": "RPlog_Snips_and_Snails",
 "title": "Snips and Snails",
 "summary": "Hidden in a seaside cave on Imperial-occupied Caspar, the Jedi pilot Leo and the newly eleven-year-old fugitive girl Gabi share a crude breakfast of fire-roasted snails and crab while waiting for a chance to escape the planet. Leo reveals a plan: the Empire's recent reinforcements have brought TIE Defenders with hyperdrives, one of which they could steal to flee and bring back help for Gabi's captured mother. Gabi, guarded and wise beyond her years, confesses she saw a sad, silent vision of her mother in the cave and rages at the Empire for keeping them from going home. Leo calms her with the Jedi Code and assures her that her mother is buying them time, and the girl resolves to swallow her grief, embrace her mother's fierce temper, and help steal a fighter to save her.",
